Template: apache2-web-conf/domain_name
Type: string
default:  $${HOSTNAME}.lan
Description: Primary domain name for this server:
 Please provide the domain name of this server. This will be used to configure the apache virtual hosts
 and SSL certificates. Be aware that this information can be provided, extended and or edited later. 

Template: apache2-web-conf/remote_ips
Type: string
default:
Description: List of any remote IP addresses that requier 'dev.' access:
 Please provide a space seperated list of additional IP addresses that you would wish to
 gain remote access. Be aware that this information can be provided, extended and or edited later.
